node.text:
Super excited to share my collaboration with DIRECTV STREAM. Whether I’m on the road or at home with my family, I can watch my favorite movies and channels with the best of live TV and on demand. Speaking of movies, @gal_gadot and I got together to show you just how amazing it can be when you get all the entertainment you love together. 🎾💥🤖

#GetYourTVTogether @directv #Ad
